import React from 'react'
import FirstSection from '../components/LightShow/FirstSection'
import SecondSection from '../components/LightShow/SecondSection'
import ThirdSection from '../components/LightShow/ThirdSection'
import FourthSection from '../components/LightShow/FourthSection'
import Footer from '../components/Footer/Footer'
const LightShow = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <FirstSection />

    <ThirdSection />
    <SecondSection />
    <FourthSection />
    <Footer />
    </>
  )
}

export default LightShow
